{"type": "article", "id": 33914, "title": "又一个韩妆品牌进入美国，以及，COS2017春夏系列发布 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2016-10-31T03:06:05Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 248, "name": "COS"}, {"id": 17255, "name": "KITH"}, {"id": 34446, "name": "韩妆品牌"}, {"id": 1231, "name": "PUMA"}, {"id": 18545, "name": "Tag Heuer"}, {"id": 20947, "name": "Too Cool for School"}, {"id": 34447, "name": "Solebox"}, {"id": 34448, "name": "Hanesbrands"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 25, "image": "img/article/article_show/20161031102002asQiOWrPL6DM21gC.jpg", "contents": "<h3>一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/beauty-industry-news/retailing/too-cool-for-school-soho-flagship-retail-10692896/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>韩妆品牌 Too Cool for School 开设美国首店</b></a> |  Too Cool for School 品牌的办公地在纽约，但是研发和制作机构在韩国。在上周五， Too Cool for School 开设了它在美国的首家旗舰店，这个店位于曼哈顿  Lafayette 街，有 Too Cool for School 的 12 支产品线中的 11 支在店内出售。 Too Cool for School 现在在韩国有 39 家门店，在中国、日本及马来西亚地区均有店铺。品牌计划通过曼哈顿首家实现美国地区 40 家门店的扩张，另外，下一步将通过 Sephora 专柜进入欧洲市场。</p><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/markets/hanesbrands-q3-results-meet-wall-street-estimates-10692998/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>美国最大的内衣制造商 Hanesbrands 第三季度收入达预期</b></a> | 作为美国最大的内衣制造商，Hanesbrands 的第三季度净收入上涨了 7.2%，达 1.739 亿美元。总营收上涨了 10.7%，达 17.6 亿美元，达到华尔街此前的预期。HanesBrands 在过去的三年中，在首席运营官 Gerald Evans 的带领下，公司成功地进行了 6 次大手笔并购。&nbsp;</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p>德国著名的球鞋店铺<a href=\"http://www.highsnobiety.com/2016/10/30/solebox-vienna/\" rel=\"nofollow\"> Solebox 于奥地利首都维也纳开设了当地首家门店</a>。这家店铺分为两层，在入口处摆放了多幅以球鞋为灵感的画作。地下的那一层墙身以木头设计，并用不规则的石头来当座椅，看起来就像是进入了一个布满球鞋的隧道一般。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161031101553guyFVpkcD0TLxwr9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161031101604qOaJvIB2L4sSAFHy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161031101604JvWeibQRokrqFtOE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610311016049pZN5lBGqEaPb8Iu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161031101613JPVUW2BrwKYTI8f3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">秋冬季想要穿得硬朗一点，来看看纽约街头名店<a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/10/kith-2016-fall-2nd-delivery-lookbook\" rel=\"nofollow\"> KITH 的 2016 秋季 Classics 系列</a>最后一波造型指南。该系列包括人气单品 Bomber、鱼尾大衣和工装裤，简约舒适又不失型格。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161031101528xQfg8qp01reN3A9G.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610311015286NxYDPAQ8syMGVcj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666250\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610311015280FSPzErMbOod5ing.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161031101529KUCJvXSmjzV963lq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016103110152924Ug5yCVDzNex9XL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161031101529X497NUtDRAQvuc6i.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161031101542W3iKDTQL9kSPUcoj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666250\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161031101542WL4miahBVMS9PJwv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666250\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">为纪念拳王阿里，瑞士名表 TAG Heuer 推出名为 <a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/10/tag-heuer-carrera-calibre-5-ring-master-tribute-to-muhammad-ali\" rel=\"nofollow\">Tribute to Muhammad Ali </a>的纪念款腕表，同时附上一对拳王亲笔签名的拳击手套、纪念奖章，全部装在特别设计的瑞士制鉚钉皮革表盒之内。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610311014538vJsrtIYGpqWUHRm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161031101504GUhuC6074V2NODEr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161031101510WEKlTAIMP1HQVxvN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610311015119SCZlbjg62YnrAMw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">在和 Agnes Martin 合作引起热烈反响之后，<a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/10/cos-2017-ss-collection\" rel=\"nofollow\">COS 继续发布它的 2017 春夏系列</a>。在该系列中 COS 延续了它的简约设计，以橄榄绿、白、灰、浅蓝、深蓝、咖啡等色调为主，男装和女装的款式都还不错。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161031101418iS3FJlegdaKTcrDG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161031101418P1xA6aJiSOgkZsMQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161031101418Vt1AyXTSM8xQwOdK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161031101418Ep3S2CIa7ArRNQqW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161031101418hlIAJQKYXbHwgEUR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161031101418mWycsSTb8OpkE5UB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016103110142420YJxRvdVfG1u6SE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161031101431irhjPRp3gyTY1064.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://sneakernews.com/2016/10/28/atmos-puma-clyde-tattoo-ichibay-collab/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Puma 与东京球鞋专门店 atmos 及刺青艺术专家 ICHIBAY 进行三方合作</a>，以 Clyde 鞋为蓝本，打造全新的和风鞋款系列。除了球鞋之外，该系列还有同样充满日式风情的 T-shirt、卫衣及袜款，将于 11 月 3 日正式发售。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161031101336VQKIoDRP2dlTY9zq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161031101344O5m2dGDsWx6A0pny.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610311013444UALa3S6dMTQsn7p.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161031101344bqtCGUlPJe6Y4uK9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161031101344Fpa1mt6cb4nWKYeR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610311013523T0n9CoQzjmAUb6B.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161031101359OLzoUqcga2tsZKMh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161031101359Rbk1fNrhyW7p9dit.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">&nbsp;<br></p>"}